{"tid":2238270,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"不要把特斯拉當車企看，潛在的能源巨頭才是正解","createTime":"2020-10-11T04:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T01:06:04.000Z","uid":295230,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b2bedbbf2d11d89ef8da990d8e1bbcec5d063fb4","tid":2238270,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:14:25.000Z","msg":"風險投資家Chamath Palihapitiya最近在一檔節目中表示，特斯拉 &nbsp;(NASDAQ:TSLA)是一家&ldquo;普遍被錯誤估價&rdquo;的公司，人們繼續誤解其&ldquo;從根本上具有顛覆性&rdquo;的技術和商業模式。<br />\n&ldquo;特斯拉繼續被低估，&rdquo;這位投資家表示，&ldquo;我認爲，人們對它的估價是錯誤的。試圖與特斯拉競爭的人並不是它的對手。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n他強調，特斯拉&ldquo;不再專注于汽車業務&rdquo;，&ldquo;這項業務的價值在于解除對能源的管制&rdquo;。他指出，需要注意的是，這家公司生産電池和能源存儲系統，可能會顛覆能源企業。<br />\n<br />\nPalihapitiya認爲，電池日上展示的電池技術的最新發展意義重大。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;創新的陰極、陽極、電池包裝&hellip;我能告訴你的是，這些人展示的是一個有意義的飛躍和創新。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我是一個投資者，也是爲這個電氣化供應鏈提供原料的稀土所有者。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nPalihapitiya表示，多年來，人們一直認爲汽車巨頭將超過特斯拉，但它們制造的電動汽車只有少數在市場上取得成功。基本上，汽車公司都在混日子。與此同時，特斯拉生産的電動汽車越來越多。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;現實情況是，特斯拉每季度出貨的汽車越來越多，&rdquo;Palihapitiya補充道。&ldquo;消費者的需求越來越大，而特斯拉擁有一個簡化的平台，使該公司能夠獲得比競爭對手更高的單位産品利潤率。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n這位投資家還表示，特斯拉&ldquo;將成爲世界上最有價值的公司之一&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"1f6058466c0263ace2031cead2fcaafc70fe73ba","tid":2238270,"uid":316420,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:27:50.000Z","msg":"繼續燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272a30b44dbf77a290bec6db0dd46cc59f27d60a","tid":2238270,"uid":14867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:33:07.000Z","msg":"將energy generation decentralize 先可以令窮國家有穩定電力供應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530c29d4c44b7ee8d549e6d7acfff8ab7e7e1f38","tid":2238270,"uid":88878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:46:22.000Z","msg":"潛力無限 提升至孖爆買入評級<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb868e5cf03d54cfb86f0c8dd805ab21aa489e4","tid":2238270,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:23:31.000Z","msg":"俾人一抄就玩撚完啦"},{"pid":"9d21752463c548bc7585fcc127361072c0965c27","tid":2238270,"uid":55533,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"我們在美國的父，願人都尊你的名為鋼鐵俠，願你的space X降臨，願你的model X，行在地上，如同starlink行在天上。我們晚晚炒的美股，今日分拆給我們；用Neuralink接上我們的大腦，如同我們接上電腦的接口。不要叫我們遇見熊市，救我們脫離貧窮；因為火星，地球，月球，全是你的，直到永遠。阿門。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7ad43dba09d1ad1ceccce181dddb257b1116df","tid":2238270,"uid":105219,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ccb868e5cf03d54cfb86f0c8dd805ab21aa489e4","tid":2238270,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:23:31.000Z","msg":"俾人一抄就玩撚完啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:05:51.000Z","msg":"工藝嘅嘢，唔係話抄就抄到，好似光刻機, CPU, NGS， 光學鏡片等等技術， 就算畀你知道點樣製作，你抄到功能， 抄唔到質素"},{"pid":"811b88634e9a42c35809bd8ea39a8f10ff28bc88","tid":2238270,"uid":220309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:07:41.000Z","msg":"靜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3f85c679a8eea520f07088601220a5a6f35a66","tid":2238270,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccb868e5cf03d54cfb86f0c8dd805ab21aa489e4","tid":2238270,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:23:31.000Z","msg":"俾人一抄就玩撚完啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:07:56.000Z","msg":"咁易抄咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e755cdea8f324db17505c67975981ea9847fb1","tid":2238270,"uid":175523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccb868e5cf03d54cfb86f0c8dd805a